  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">HelpAge provides older people with healthcare and nutritional education in collaboration with other NGOs and other public and private health institutions.

Support older people with health insurance coverage for six months.

The project trains student nurses on the age-specific health issues that older people face.

Continue with networking, advocating for and supporting affordable healthcare for older people, including cholera prevention, ophthalmological and psycho-social care

HelpAge continues to provide long-term residential care to older people in nursing homes.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project supports, advice and advocate to government and private providers regarding adequate standard of care for older people in residential homes.</narrative>
